Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.98,0:00:03.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,終於…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:06.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,年末衝刺終於要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.06,0:00:08.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,年末衝刺是指
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:11.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,編輯部為了在新年期間休息個夠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:15.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在年內只要沒拿到原稿就會鞭策漫畫家的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:16.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,惡魔行徑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.91,0:00:19.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,得一點點地提前幹完工作才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:21.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:23.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還真是樂觀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:25.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那當然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:28.09,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord0\fad(500,0)\pos(744,264)}豪談社 感謝晚會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:28.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為有豪談社的年末晚會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:33.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師  晚會請帶上羅砂我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:34.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不要學小南說話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:34.93,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：指漫畫「棒球英豪」女主人公淺倉南  著名台詞「請帶我去甲子園」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:36.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我才不去  麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:40.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不要學小南哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:43.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,去不了晚會的話  就沒法努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:45.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不知道努力還有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:47.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你…你們為何會這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:51.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,平時一直宅在工作室  見不到陽光的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.44,0:00:53.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是被招待至晚會的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.94,0:00:57.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就能感受到「啊我們還在這個業界裡」的實感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:02.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以請帶上我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:03.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我知道了  我知道了快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.54,0:01:06.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒了哦  晚會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.71,0:01:10.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,由於出版不景氣導致了經費削減
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:13.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以今年改為在居酒屋或卡拉OK定包間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:16.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,每本雜誌分開舉行的小型慰勞會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:20.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,居酒屋和…卡拉OK…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.72,0:01:23.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那些傢伙肯定會很失落的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:25.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是也不是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:27.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.85,0:01:29.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師  真是令人期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:31.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,酒店的晚會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:33.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我買好晚會的服裝了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:35.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我買好數碼相機了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.36,0:01:41.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的  我有件隱瞞之事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:44.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:45.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,派對沒了這件事
