Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:40.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,上週剛畫完聖誕回  所以有種結束了的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:43.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,枝形吊燈我也好好裝飾上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:47.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個是…舞廳球燈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:50.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是枝形吊燈麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:54.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為  我還沒見過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:56.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大概只是因為你不記得了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:58.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小的枝形吊燈大概有在街上見過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.50,0:04:00.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:04.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好想看看啊  大的枝形吊燈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:08.68,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz334\pos(972.8,620.8)}臘月是你的謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:08.68,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：標題源自新川直司漫畫「四月是你的謊言」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:11.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大的枝形吊燈不是有的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:14.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在晚會現場有個巨大的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:18.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是帶上小姬的話能看到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:20.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:24.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也是呢  這樣漫畫家身份肯定會暴露呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:27.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,作為代替就由我們就看個夠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:30.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,去拍下高解析度的照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:34.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  你們也看不到枝形吊燈了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,話說  這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:40.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是資料  這週要畫正月段子對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:44.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有時候都不知道自己身處哪個時空了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:47.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,實際上聖誕節都還沒到呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:50.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,幾週前就過完了的聖誕節再過一次什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:53.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,簡直就像時空穿越者一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:56.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:59.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,聖誕節還沒來麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  像小孩一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:02.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還早著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:04.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:07.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這不讓姬知道我是時空穿越者的演技
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:09.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:10.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.70,0:05:14.08,kakushigoto text - 2,,0,0,0,,\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h師走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:14.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一瞬之間的事呢  畢竟是「臘月」了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:14.08,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：12月的別稱，日語中為「師走」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:16.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,臘月？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:21.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,師  也就是說這是連老師都會跑起來的匆忙時期
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:23.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:28.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的耶  老師跑起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:31.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一子老師平時也在跑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:36.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,反過來說現在這個時期跑起來的人全都是老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:40.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,跑起來的人一定都是老師啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:43.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師是指學校的老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:47.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,被叫做「老師」的人不是有很多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:51.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,像是醫生  政治家以及藝術家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:51.70,kakushigoto in 10,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs50\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H260002&\pos(1457.6,752)}醫（師）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:51.70,kakushigoto in 10,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fad(300,0)\fs50\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H260002&\pos(833.6,752)}政治家（老師）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:51.70,kakushigoto in 10,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fad(300,0)\fs50\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H260002&\pos(264,750.4)}藝術家（老師）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:53.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還有漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師  快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:06:01.33,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\c&HC363F4&\3c&HF4F7FE&\move(880,44.8,1134,44.8)}乃村坂46展覽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:06:00.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師  奇蹟般的還有剩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:02.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不愧是老師  果然有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,稱號是「老師」的人真多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖然大都是帶有嘲弄的意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:12.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,編輯稱漫畫家「老師」也是蔑稱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:15.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還沒畫完麼  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:19.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,喂喂大老師  又要減頁了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:21.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大都是帶著戲謔的意思在用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:23.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:25.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:26.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你們無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:28.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然後在成為老手後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:30.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,蔑稱更是升級為「巨匠」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這種情況下通常會帶上地名去叫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:36.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,編輯都是些社會精英
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:41.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以肯定會產生「區區漫畫家還這麼拽」的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是被害妄想麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:44.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:47.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對真正的巨匠  是不會以「巨匠」去稱呼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:48.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,狀態如何呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:51.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,巨匠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:53.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,現在說的就是這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:58.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即便如此會被稱作老師的身份還是挺令人憧憬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:01.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我懂  作為一個微不足道的助手來說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:04.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  我們有那個東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:08.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只要站在那兒  就沉浸在了自己是老師的感覺之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:10.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,年末的晚會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,咦  還沒聽說麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:14.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,快住口！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:22.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你竟敢說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:25.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我到底犯了什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:26.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,已經不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:28.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,努力不下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:30.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,失去了活下去的希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:33.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,晚會沒了什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:37.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  這淚水的巧克力噴泉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:40.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,幹勁異常低下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:43.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣是熬不過年末衝刺的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:51.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這兒有取回幹勁的唯一手段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:53.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:56.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,出席中學館的晚會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:57.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:00.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那邊還是在酒店舉行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:03.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是…最近完全沒有接活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:07.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,認識的擔任責編也都人事變動到其他地方了不會來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:07.46,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\frz270\c&HD89BF3&\3c&H8E55D8&\pos(64,238.4)}時尚部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:07.46,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\pos(468.8,28.8)\c&HD8EFCC&\3c&H6A8751&}繪本部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:07.46,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\c&H685BE7&\3c&H0B127C&\pos(1297.6,12.8)}營業部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:07.46,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\frz270\c&HE4E5A5&\3c&HB6926D&\pos(1699.2,244.8)}其他公司
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:10.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,誰都不認識我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:11.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,很尷尬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:13.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可以帶上小姬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:19.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不如說沒人認識的話漫畫家的事情也不會暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:22.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還能讓小姬看到大的枝形吊燈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:27.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「我在會舉辦這種晚會的公司裡上班」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:29.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,作為爸爸的威嚴也能保住哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:32.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,作為爸爸的…威嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:38.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好的大家  要去中學館的晚會囉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:39.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:40.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:43.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師…被忽悠了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:44.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,正常想的話風險很高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:46.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也想去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:47.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:50.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其他公司的編輯在場的話會被警戒的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:52.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,警戒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:53.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為啥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:56.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,會被認為是來挖角的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:59.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那不是提升業績的好機會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:00.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,請帶上我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,想都別想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:04.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而且還是同一天舉辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:07.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你啊  自己公司的不去是鬧哪樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:12.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我才不想去居酒屋卡拉OK這些寒酸的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:12.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,輪不到你說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:16.07,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\c&H5A48CD&\frx12\fry350\frz22.37\org(956.8,102.4)\pos(406.4,91.2)}周刊少年漫畫人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:16.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後藤老師也不參加麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:19.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,人太少了會辦不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:21.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,找誰都行  開口去問問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:23.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,誰都行麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:28.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有枝形吊燈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:31.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是啊  爸爸的公司要舉辦晚會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:32.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬也一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:33.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,派對？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:35.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,派對人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:36.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是派對人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:39.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是呢  爸爸和姬都是派對人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:41.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可以帶上納德拉小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:43.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我喜歡熱鬧點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:45.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:48.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那爸爸和公司的人一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:51.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬就由納德拉小姐帶著在當地匯合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:58.53,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\c&H3B3D4C&\pos(259.2,452.8)}晚會當天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:01.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬小姐  我把這個收好了就要出發去晚會了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:03.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,知道了  我去準備下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:06.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,納德拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:08.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,CEO？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:11.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個  是晚會的請帖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:13.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可以的話請務必
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:15.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後藤先生那兒的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:16.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,已經聽說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那就恭候光臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:25.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:27.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,衣帽間那兒也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:29.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然該一起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:32.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你在做什麼哦  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:35.15,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\bord2\c&H382BA7&\3c&HD7F0FA&\pos(686.4,345.6)}卡拉OK  宴會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:35.15,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\bord4\c&HA1D6FB&\3c&H767C76&\pos(646.4,710.4)}順其自然度假地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:39.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在這邊  等你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:41.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,納德拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:42.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:44.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬也？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:46.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:50.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後藤老師也要來這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:51.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬在那邊的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:52.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:56.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太好了…才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:59.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是去漫畫人那邊的晚會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:01.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是漫畫家的事情就會暴露給姬了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:02.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:06.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,枝形吊燈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:09.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然我是對的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:15.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說是爸爸馬上就會到你身邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:20.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸他？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:27.45,kakushigoto in 5 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\c&H1F1610&\frz280.2\1a&H29&\pos(192,510.4)}師走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:27.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  跑起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:28.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:29.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:33.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸是老師麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:35.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:37.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不…不是的  肯定有什麼誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:39.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸才不是老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:41.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是剛剛跑起來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:42.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:46.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個人不是什麼老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:48.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是巨匠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:52.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是老師而是巨匠哦  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:54.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,巨匠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:56.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,巨匠是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:12:01.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是…一種公司職位  就類似課長部長這種
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:04.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,誒  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:07.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果你不是老師那就不能亂跑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:08.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還不回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:13.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不然我們進不去晚會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:19.00,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord6\fs65\frz357.2\c&HCAA278&\3c&HF0F3E2&\pos(753.6,392)}中學館漫畫交流會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:26.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣  這就是我想讓姬你看的巨大枝形吊燈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:27.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:30.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但其實這是「灰姑娘燈」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:35.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太漂亮了  所以它是灰姑娘燈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:39.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是的…雖然讀起來確實很像啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:39.27,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：日語的吊燈和灰姑娘發音有點像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:42.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為它很像灰姑娘穿的裙子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:44.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,確實有點像  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:50.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我懂的  小時候我也以為那就是灰姑娘燈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:53.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒想到你還有小女生的一面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為什麼你會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:56.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我跟著你們來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:59.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不太好吧  你就這樣擅自進來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:02.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是來給後藤老師送東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:05.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我就是以這個藉口混進來找些人氣作者挖下牆腳的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:08.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你心裡想的全說出來了
