Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:13.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,再說了  你怎麼從這麼多人中分辨出誰是漫畫家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:16.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,穿著邋遢的人自然是漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您還真敢斷言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:19.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也有可能是助手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其實很簡單的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:28.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,出版社都不會將人氣漫畫家放一邊  責編都會緊跟著的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:33.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,責編都是負責接待的  所以要求他們穿西裝打領帶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:34.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:39.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,身邊有穿西裝的護衛且打扮邋遢的人  就一定是人氣漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:40.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真敢斷言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:42.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:45.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖然你也說打扮邋遢的人是漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:49.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可是現如今  少年雜誌中有人氣的漫畫家基本都是女性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:52.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這人真是有話就敢說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:54.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果是女性畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:58.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,總會穿些和年齡不符少女風的輕飄飄服飾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:13:59.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:03.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那我就找身邊有穿西裝的護衛且穿著輕飄飄的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:04.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:06.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,請您一定要來鄙社工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:11.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:15.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,身邊有穿西裝的護衛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:17.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,且穿著輕飄飄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:19.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:20.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您落下的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:21.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,滾過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:27.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我長這麼大還沒有人這麼罵過我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:29.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不對的是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:32.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,才不是  後藤老師才是最不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:35.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,區區一個漫畫家  居然穿西裝打領帶來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:39.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫畫家就該打扮得像漫畫家一樣邋遢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:42.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但您不覺得慶幸自己搭話的對象是後藤老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:47.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要真的是漫畫家和責編的話  你早就被暴打一頓了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:53.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我總感覺那人在哪裡看過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:55.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是我想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:59.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可要小心像那樣來路不明的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:01.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我知道他是什麼人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:03.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:05.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,糟了  居然收下了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:09.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他好像是個出版書的公司員工
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:10.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:13.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.59,0:15:16.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我又不像小千田那樣可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:18.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:22.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我可成為不了讀者模特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:24.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,讀者模特？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:28.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原來如此  她是以為自己被星探挖去當雜誌的讀者模特了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:34.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒那回事  姬這麼可愛  完全能勝任的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:35.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,哄我的話就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:37.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,才不是哄你的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:41.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那爸爸替你保管名片吧  等到你有那個想法的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:47.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個  這個  這個  這個  還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:50.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,從文娛公司到童星公司
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:52.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的被星探給發現了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:54.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什麼時候發生的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:16:00.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,難道是我把姬給帶進了這個危險狼窩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:03.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖說是漫畫交流會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:05.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只要雜誌上還有封面女郎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:09.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就會有尋找封面女郎的星探
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:13.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就會有想將漫畫動畫化或真人化的節目組人員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:17.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今天是這些魑魅魍魎聚集的安息日了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:21.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這裡已經不再是只有責編和漫畫家的簡單世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:25.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不對  說起來漫畫家這群人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:27.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不全員都是蘿莉控嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:29.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們要回去了  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.96,0:16:32.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是十丸院的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:34.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,滾過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:35.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那時候掉的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:37.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有間諜  是講談社的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:38.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.85,0:16:41.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,居然敢潛入我們的晚會  居心叵測
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:46.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,肯定是來挖牆腳的  趕快找出他  那個講談社叫十丸院的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:48.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬  你稍微在這裡等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:50.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可不要收名片哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:52.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,十丸院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:55.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,別罵了  別罵了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:57.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你潛入這裡的事已經暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:00.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你會被中學館的人帶去吊死的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:03.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣啊  我做了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:04.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你還嫌你做得不夠多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:07.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,總之  在被發現之前你趕緊離開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:09.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:11.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,出口已經被嚴加看管了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:14.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但長相還沒有暴露吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:15.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:18.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,Facebook上  臉漏了個精光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:22.77,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\c&HEA81EE&\move(688,56,691,246)}十丸院五月先生的夏日夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:21.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,想必早就暴露了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:22.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,已經無路可走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:24.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,去認罪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:25.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:29.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還有一個能夠逃脫的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,打扮成漫畫家就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:34.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫畫家?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:36.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:39.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果是漫畫家的話  就算是行為有些怪異也不太好檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:40.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:42.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,現在就準備一些能夠派上用場的周邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:48.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:53.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真像漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:55.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不管從哪裡看上去都是漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.42,0:17:59.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼感覺連我也被貶低了  是我的錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:02.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,現在可不是笑的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:05.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,得趕緊幫助他離開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:10.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師  雖然您總是罵我  原來您還是為我著想的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:15.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是這傢伙被抓住了  連我也要被當成從犯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:17.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,趕緊走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:18.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:22.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,得趕緊帶姬離開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:24.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在變態的魔爪伸向她之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:26.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也許是那個漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:27.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,或許又是那個漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:30.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,肯定都是變態
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:35.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這人的眼神猶如獵人一般  在上下打量著我社的漫畫家們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:36.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一定沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:39.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你就是十丸院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:41.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你…你認錯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:45.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:48.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,剛從姬那裡接管的名片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:50.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:53.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,找到了  在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:55.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,別讓他逃了  可惡的講談社
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:59.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬  我們去另外一邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:01.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:05.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是後藤老…課長的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:08.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你有什麼臉來我們這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:09.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你這漫畫人的混蛋責編
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:13.50,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}抓  打
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:12.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是的  我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:15.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:16.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,少騙人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:18.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫畫家怎麼可能穿西裝打領帶來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:27.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,難道我就這麼被冤枉  吊死在中學館本部嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:28.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:32.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這不後藤嗎  好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:35.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小瀨鱷先生  好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:38.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他就那個畫風之內褲的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:38.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是緊身褲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:41.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的是多有得罪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你的西裝我們會賠償的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:46.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:48.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,暫且先用這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:52.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是漫畫家誒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:53.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:57.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果再穿件外套的話就不會被姬發現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:20:00.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對了  我得趕緊帶姬離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:02.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,羅砂她在另一邊照看著姬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:04.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬——
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:06.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,哎呀後藤老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:09.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原來您也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:12.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說起來  你們兩位為什麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:14.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們也稍微來露個面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:21.53,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz253.1\bord4\c&HE9EAB1&\3c&HBEA577&\pos(1429.8,348.8)}最近不好賣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:21.53,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz278.6\bord4\c&HEAECB3&\3c&HBE9D72&\pos(830.4,180.8)}大家都是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:19.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的沒關係嗎  漫畫人的編輯來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:21.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畢竟現如今是這個世道了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:23.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,又不能和別人起爭執
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:25.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,上邊的人也相互之間有往來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:28.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,究竟是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:35.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然一到晚上就很冷啊  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:36.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是…是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:39.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你外套忘了拿了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.21,0:20:44.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師的外套真暖和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:47.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:49.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你要用我的圍巾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:51.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:53.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,比起這個  今天玩開心了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:56.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯  灰姑娘燈好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:21:00.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好大好閃亮  太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:01.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:04.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:05.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:10.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:13.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,比灰姑娘燈還厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:15.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這就是超級灰姑娘燈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:23.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為了這一笑容  我會繼續隱瞞下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:26.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是漫畫家這一事實
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.85,0:21:39.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:43.19,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}消失了的漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:47.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,共計800元
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:53.12,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}後藤可久士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:54.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.54,0:22:00.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是騙人的吧
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,——————ED——————
