Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:24.11,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}架子十足地撅起嘴唇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:30.95,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}何かたくらむ表情は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:30.95,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}正在盤算著什麼企圖的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.28,0:22:36.08,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}別れの気配を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.28,0:22:36.08,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}將離別的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:45.84,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}ポケットに匿していたから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:45.84,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}隱藏在口袋中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.13,0:22:52.93,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}想い出は  モノクローム
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.13,0:22:52.93,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}回憶是單色相片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:58.48,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}色を点けてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:58.48,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}給我點上顏色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:06.73,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}もう一度  そばに来て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:06.73,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}再一次來到我的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.90,0:23:11.78,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}はなやいで  うるわしの Color Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.90,0:23:11.78,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}花枝招展的  美麗的Color Girl
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.88,0:23:33.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師  您要死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:37.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為了姬爸爸能夠早日康復  大家來許願吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.14,0:23:40.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,新年假期去海外的漫畫家全是垃圾
